metadata.name: The little prince & the tree of life
metadata.description:
Little tale, at what point did you manage to adapt to my life?, you changed as you please, and became my reality.
I feel as if life came to the point of asking the tree of life for my true meaning of being here.
I dream one day to join all the people who have crossed your leaves, but first i need to complete the tasks what im here for.

5120 x 5120 px

Made with Photoshop, Stable Diffusion, procreate and my Soul.
